WEBVTT

00:03:59.322 --> 00:04:03.527
where you create a building

00:04:03.551 --> 00:04:06.339
and it becomes alive with light?

00:04:07.522 --> 00:04:11.540
Like alabaster, if you kiss it with light,
it becomes alive.

00:04:11.564 --> 00:04:13.706
And I drew this sketch,

00:04:13.730 --> 00:04:17.091
something with two layers, translucent

00:04:17.115 --> 00:04:19.872
with structure in between capturing light.

00:04:20.646 --> 00:04:26.607
Maybe a pure form,
a single form of emanation

00:04:26.631 --> 00:04:29.052
that you could imagine

00:04:29.076 --> 00:04:32.580
would be all dome